### Run Amazon search test
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "run_test",
  "args": { "test": "tests/test_amazon_search.py" }
}

### Create a generated test
POST http://127.0.0.1:5000/mcp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "create_test",
  "args": {
    "name": "test_search_camera",
    "steps": [
      {"action": "search", "value": "camera"}
    ]
  }
}
